body:
**Hello, I'm having issues in-game with sliding lag.** My ping is always at the normal number for me: **around 80.** But in-game I repeatedly have periods of lag that I can't seem to control. They can get so bad that I disconnect, and sometimes I'll just manually disconnect and reconnect to see if it helps, but it doesn't {{champion:32}} 

These periods of lag include not being able to see any ability or attack animations and units losing their health bars but not going through the dying animations. The game usually catches up around 20 seconds later, causing every single animation to play at once, then it just starts lagging again.

**Are there any known solutions to this problem?** Any help/advice would be greatly appreciated. Thanks {{summoner:31}}
